{"tid":1957054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府上年拍嘅「與暴力割蓆」同「珍惜香港」垃圾廣告用咗354萬","createTime":"2020-04-03T15:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T20:03:56.000Z","uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"24b19d229ad8209153963154c119eac8c8b4100b","tid":1957054,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"OMDB：<br />\n<br />\n【冇人想睇嘅廣告】狂燒納稅人354萬<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞處回覆我針對嗰堆咩「珍惜香港  與暴力割席」的廣告片段的開支時，回覆如下：<br />\n<br />\n「於2019年8月 2020年1月期間先後推出了包括中英文版的6套電視宣傳短片和電台宣傳聲帶；以及1套網上宣傳短片，旨在呼籲市民與暴力割席。短片亦呼籲市民要認清是非黑白、切勿違法，應該一起回歸理性，加強社會的凝聚力，珍惜香港這個由每位市民努力建立的家。相關的製作費合共約247萬元.....新聞處亦透過社交媒體平台在 Facebook、Instagram和 YouTube推廣上述推出的一系列電視宣傳短片及網上宣傳短片，並於港鐵站內展示宣傳海報，涉及的廣告費用合共約100萬元；而其他海報印刷費用約7萬元。」<br />\n<br />\n#與暴力地花費公帑割席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDC9h3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDC9h3O.jpg&h=f0711247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ead945c5963b699a645c057f098961e9198034","tid":1957054,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf40a474852566f0b0bb0ea106771afcf1d6e5d5","tid":1957054,"uid":189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"冇記錯好似係PowerPoint 質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb3532e493aaf43de3525dd08d4bbed1bdcd757","tid":1957054,"uid":21141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"完全冇effect<br />\n幾隻字貼上去zoom大zoom細就拎幾百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9df63c0c12836212cd5fd2f5ac7f0a104ba551","tid":1957054,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=